    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait sorry, what did you mean by the goblin thing? i'm just trying to learn the aero stuff for my exam. can you just stick to the physics of the wind shear and jet streams? how exactly do those cause the turbulence if there aren't any clouds there to show it?",
